Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.50,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}バイバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.55,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}また明日ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.67,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}やっと解放された
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.98,Dial_JP2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}これから部活なんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.40,Dial_JP2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}さあ　帰ろう帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.43,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}木戸間先生　さようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.60,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BYE BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.19,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ねぇねぇ　今から何か食べてかない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.67,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}テスト期間中行けなかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.28,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}行く行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:25.11,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新しくできたカレー屋さんはどう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:27.42,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それいいね　行こっか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.50,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}楽しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:29.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よし　これで全部だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.30,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よくかき集めたにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:41.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これで秘密基地作れますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:45.83,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}床板に壁屋根　だいたいまかなえるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}たぶんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.60,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}気持ちいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:58.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}で　結局どうするつもりよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:02.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}TAB ツリーアタッチメントボルトとか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.45,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部費で足りない分をどうするかだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}しかたない　やっぱりこれで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.01,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}HA？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.38,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.87,Dial_JP2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}いいですね　海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.73,Dial_JP2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}うみ　うみ　うみ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.52,Dial_JP2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}みんなでお出かけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.51,Dial_JP2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}うみ　うみ　うみ　うみ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:19.54,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}お金の話がなんで海に行く話になるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:23.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なんでだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.78,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Thank you Pudding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.40,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今日の授業もおもしろかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい　はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}特に量子超越性のいろいろな解釈が…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}寝ようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:18.88,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}慣れない肉体労働でホント疲れた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}じゃあ　私も寝ようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.47,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}くらげさん　明日の天気は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.33,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明日は晴れ時々曇り
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.69,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}予想最高気温25℃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.30,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}カラッと晴れた爽やかな一日となるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:36.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海へ行くにはいい日ね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:36.99,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.28,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.75,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}私も行こうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勉強は？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.21,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中間テストも終わったし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}課題はあるけど　気分転換もいいかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いいですね　海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.58,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海といえばご存じのとおり私のモデルは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.44,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海の生物がモチーフとなっているんです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.60,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青い空　白い雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:00.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}じゃ　朝９時に出発よ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good night Pudding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.05,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ちゃんとハンモックで寝なさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.43,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}オッケー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.97,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぜひとも一度は本物の海を訪れてみたいもの…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}じゃ　いってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}See you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.79,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いってらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}留守番はお任せください
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:25.86,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}心躍るようなお土産をお待ちしておりま…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.98,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おはよー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.87,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}せるふ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.13,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:36.97,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Puddingも行くって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.96,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}せるふと一緒なんて聞いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.26,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}行こ　遅れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.62,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ちょっ…ちょっと　せるふ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.74,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いい天気でよかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:50.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}た…確かにいい天気だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.95,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}っていうか　ちょっと放しなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}須理出っちとお出かけなんてうれしいにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:07.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}DIY部の活動だったとはなんでそれを言わないの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}しーちゃんがぷりんと友達だったなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.25,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ミラクルだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.25,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何がミラクル
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.30,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}で　DIY部がなんで海へ行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拾うの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.58,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}貝殻とか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}流木　シーグラス
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}DIYに使えそうなものをいろいろとね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:32.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そ…それでペンダントとかブローチなどの小物を作って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:36.69,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}売って秘密基地を作る資金の足しにするってことらしいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あくまで活動の一環だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既製品じゃない一点もののアクセサリーは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}案外喜ばれたりするんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.88,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}へぇ　そうなんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.46,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}見て見て
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.96,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なになに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.61,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.81,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}きれい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日本の海もまあまあね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.07,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}泳ぎたい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.79,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}コラ　遊びにきたんじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:26.52,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}手分けして使えそうなものを探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あまり遠くへ行かないように
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.33,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}治子先生　何か付け加えることありますか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}貝殻やガラスの破片で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}手を切ったりしないように気をつけてくださいね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:38.92,Dial_JP,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.58,Dial_JP,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}了解にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}須理出さんもよろしくね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.39,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}は…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.65,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}では
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.65,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}各自素材集めに向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.77,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do It
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.48,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.48,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.52,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}きれい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.13,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こういうの　いくつか組み合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.75,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}アクセサリーとかにしたらかわいいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.75,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よし　もっと探すぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.52,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.08,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これも使えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.28,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こういうパイプと組み合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.86,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ちょっとしたデザインやインテリアにな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.33,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.81,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}スチームパンク
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.85,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さすが部長っち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.22,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これも何かに使えるかにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:48.12,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}天井からつるしてインテリアにどうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なんかおしゃれにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こっちはめのう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.16,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こっちはシーグラス
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.12,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good　使えそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.27,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こっちの貝殻は組み合わせて　カチューシャとかにも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.45,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なんか変な石発見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なまこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.13,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}お土産に持って帰ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:23.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}お母さんと三代目喜んでくれるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.22,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なまこの三杯酢よ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いただきまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おいし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もっといないかな　なまこ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.09,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おーい　なまこ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.07,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}アンタ何しに来たのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.50,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.03,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりんも探してなまこ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それ密猟になるんじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知らないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}だめなのかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}バイバイ　なまこ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もう捕まるなよー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.40,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まったく　せるふは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:12.35,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あんなのでDIY部やっていけるのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.32,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}変な形の木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.55,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これ何かに使えないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:29.89,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部長さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.37,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いい流木じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:40.57,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい　形がおもしろいから何かに使えないかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.81,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}その形を生かして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.81,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帽子掛けなんてどうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:52.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}でも　この流木持って帰るには大きすぎますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.59,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よし　これで持って帰れるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.39,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さすが部長…さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.81,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}手際がいいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.31,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}慣れの問題さ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}慣れ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.41,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}せるふはいつまでたっても慣れないみたいですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そうでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最近少し道具に慣れてきたみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.47,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}前よりもケガが減ったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}持って帰ってヤスリかければ使えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.89,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}残った分はもらっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.99,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あっはい　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.11,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}皆勤賞ですね　せるふさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.05,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}貝殻で指切っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.52,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:47.75,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ハル姉ちゃんのお弁当おいしいにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:51.08,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Pudding ma‘amのおはぎもおいしかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.96,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これもGood job
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よかったです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}たくさん食べてくださいね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.63,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}このあとどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.07,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}素材は結構集まったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もっと探したいです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.83,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}私も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何か更にいいもの見つかるかもしれませんし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.46,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Puddingも一緒に探すよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.63,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まあ　少しくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.25,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さすが須理出っちにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.40,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}せっかく来たから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.45,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もうちょっと探すとするか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.65,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おっ　お
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.31,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こっちだってば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}待ってよー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.88,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まっ　こんなもんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.08,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結構集まったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これだけあればいろんなものが作れるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい　楽しみです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なに作ろうかにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.57,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}じゃあ　そろそろ帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.83,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遊ぶ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:03.75,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}うん　うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:09.55,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}砂のお城作って　泳いで　日光浴して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.02,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それからそれから…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.63,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まったく　海まで来て砂のお城なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.63,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}子どもじゃあるまいし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.15,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}泳ぐっていっても水着はどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.96,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それなら大丈夫です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.93,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}こんなこともあろうかと　実は水着を着てきたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.31,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}アンタ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.59,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}その　あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.21,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}実はですね　私も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}たくみんも？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.28,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}しようがないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}じゃあ　私もつきあってあげるとするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.74,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}って　ジョブ子も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.77,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然服の下は水着よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.88,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なにが当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.76,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まあ　着てきたけどな私も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:57.77,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なによそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.16,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}しーは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.15,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.58,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}言うまでもないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}となると
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:09.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}わ…私はただ連れてこられただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.38,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水着なんて着てるわけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.36,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}着てるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:17.48,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今朝楽しそうに鏡の前でポーズとってたの見たからね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.27,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さっすが須理出っちにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.78,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}みんな考えることは同じか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.39,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりんの水着気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.06,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}見せて見せて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.35,Dial_JP2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}よいではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.35,Dial_JP2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let’s go ベイベー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}イエイ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.36,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Pudding
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水蜘蛛は持ってきてないの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.61,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}七つ道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.06,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あるわけないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.15,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ジョブ子ちゃん　すいとんの術ならあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.19,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Really
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.58,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}シュノーケルでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:54.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}位置について
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:58.82,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よーい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.79,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ど…どちらも互角です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}し　しーさんの勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.86,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}２人ともとっても速いです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:34.86,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なにやってんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.62,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暖かい日でよかったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まだちょっと水は冷たいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.19,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そうだね　気持ちいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なにしてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さっきのなまこいないかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:02.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なまこは竜宮城に連れていってくれないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.61,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}え　そっか　よくわかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:10.36,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりんは私のことなんでもお見通しだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.86,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当たり前でしょ　アンタの考えていることくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さっすが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.32,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なにが「さっすが」だか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今の言い方すごく似てた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.25,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もう1回やってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.06,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嫌よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.55,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もう1回やってみてよー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.03,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嫌ったら嫌よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.47,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Finish
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:36.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Japanese castle Good job たくみ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}2人で頑張ったかいがありましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.93,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大切なのは水分の割合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:48.32,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本当は粘土を混ぜ込むと地盤が安定するのだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.93,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}しー　そっちは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}特にこの瓦の表現が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}にゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh my gosh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これでよし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ありがとう　ぷりん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:17.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}髪結んでもらうなんて久しぶりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.40,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}自分でやったらすぐほどけちゃうし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}せるふは不器用だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.39,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今日はぷりんと一緒に来られてよかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そ…そう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.76,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.73,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ねぇ　ぷりん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.90,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりんもDIY部に入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.79,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高校は違うけどしーちゃんも入部許可されたし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:54.40,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりんも入ってくれたらまた毎日一緒に帰れるし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.36,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}カビが生えたなんて言ってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.75,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}少しはDIYに興味が出てきたんじゃないかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.52,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}でも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:06.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}でも？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.27,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おーい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.94,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}せるふっち　須理出っち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なーに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.40,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一緒に遊ぶにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.57,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}うん　今行く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}行こ　ぷりん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}私はいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.32,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}材料探しでちょっと疲れたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:37.52,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そっか　じゃあまたあとでね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:38.37,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.03,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}きれい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これせるふにあげたら喜ぶかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.04,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おい　ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.58,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}いたっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日焼け止め塗ってなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.69,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}甘いわね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:44.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}私はちゃんと準備してたから平気よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.54,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もう海なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.12,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}行かなきゃよかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.94,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そんなことはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:55.12,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}楽しくないことはなかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.11,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}え？聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:10.84,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.35,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}できたにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.12,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我ながら傑作にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.12,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あとで元どおりにしておけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:19.96,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}にゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}では　シーグラスでブレスレットを作ろうと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}これに穴をあけるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.47,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:32.85,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まずはシーグラスの表面に軽く水をつけます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}なんで水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:38.26,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}シーグラスは削るとガラスの粉が舞ったり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.16,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}熱で割れやすくなったりするんです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.30,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それでは削っていきます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.38,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水が白く濁ってきたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}軽く水で流してください
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.54,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}８割くらいまで穴があいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.32,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ダイヤモンドビットを２ミリに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今度は反対側から…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.34,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}穴があいたら表面にレジン液を塗って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.66,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}UVライトで乾かします
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あとはテグスにシーグラスやビーズをとおせば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完成です
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.33,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}たくみんすごーい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ホントにお店で売ってるものみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good job たくみ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.29,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}たくみっち　やるにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:33.78,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}確かにこれならどこへ出しても恥ずかしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.11,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そ…そうですか　よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}で　どうやって売る？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}インターネット
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日本だけじゃなくて　世界中に向けて発信するにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.98,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}世界中から注文が殺到しちゃったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.20,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それは夢見すぎだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:56.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ネット以外には文化祭のバザー…は秋か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:57.77,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}フリマとか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.08,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}棚をレンタルしている雑貨屋さんがあります
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}そこで手芸品を売ったりしていて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.45,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それもありだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.23,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}待てよ　うちの店に置いてもらうこともできるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.73,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}WAKUWAKU WANWANにですか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.64,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}私行ってみたいです　ワークワン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部長っちの家行きたいにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.68,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ああ　いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.54,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}みんなで遊びにきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.27,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}やった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.67,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.29,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ちょうどいい感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.28,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初めてにしてはなかなかのものね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}あとはシーグラスと貝殻があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.76,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何かこれで置物を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:54.48,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}って　なにやってんのよ私
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.94,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勉強しなくちゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.50,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜拜
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.55,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天见
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.67,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}终于解放了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.98,Dial_CH2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}我还有社团活动
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.40,Dial_CH2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}该回家了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}木户间老师 再见
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.60,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜拜
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天见
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我说 咱去吃点啥吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.67,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}毕竟之前有考试没去成
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好啊好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.58,0:00:25.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新开的那家咖喱料理店怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.11,0:00:27.42,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听起来不错 就去那吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}期待死了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.50,0:00:29.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了 这些就是全部了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真给我累坏了喵
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.77,0:00:41.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就能做秘密基地了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.40,0:00:45.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}地板 墙壁 天花板 差不多都有了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过只是大概
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.60,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真舒服啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.60,0:00:58.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以说到底该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.21,0:01:02.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}TAB 也就是树木连接螺栓什么的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.45,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}社团预算不够的部分该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没办法 还得靠这个
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.01,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去海边吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.38,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海边?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.87,Dial_CH2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}真好啊 海边
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.73,Dial_CH2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}海边 海边 海边
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.52,Dial_CH2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}大家要一块出门咯
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.51,Dial_CH2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}海边 海边 海边 海边
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.34,0:01:19.54,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么说着说着就从钱变成海边的话题了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.21,0:01:23.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你猜
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.78,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天的课也很有意思
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}干得不错
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}特别是量子霸权的相关解释…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要睡了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.24,0:03:18.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不习惯的体力劳动把我累坏了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我也睡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水母先生 明天天气怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明日天气晴间多云
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}预计最高温度25度
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想必是风和日丽 十分爽朗的一天
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.59,0:03:36.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真适合去海边呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.27,0:03:36.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海边?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也去看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不学习吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}期中考试已经结束了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然还有课题 但转换一下心情也不错
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真不错啊 海边
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.58,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说起海洋 想必您知道
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.44,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的外观原型生物便来自于此
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.60,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}碧空如洗 英英白云
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.22,0:04:00.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那明早九点出发
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}晚安 布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}记得要好好睡在吊床上
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OK
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无论如何我也想去欣赏一次海…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 我们出发了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再见
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.79,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一路顺风
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看家请交给我
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.23,0:04:25.86,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我等着您那令人跃雀的礼…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.87,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塞璐芙
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.13,0:04:36.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}布丁说她也来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可没听说塞璐芙也来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.26,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}走吧 要迟到了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.62,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等…等等 塞璐芙
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.74,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}天气真好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.74,0:04:50.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}确…确实是好天气
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.95,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但把我放开啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和须理出亲一起出门真开心喵
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.48,0:05:07.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么不早点告诉我是DIY部的活动啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小希和布丁原来是朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是奇迹般的巧合
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哪门子奇迹
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 为什么DIY部要去海边
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}捡东西
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.58,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}捡什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}贝壳之类的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}流木 海玻璃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要能在DIY中派上用场的都行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.52,0:05:32.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用…用这些做吊坠 别针之类的小饰品
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.32,0:05:36.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后卖了来补足秘密基地的制作资金
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说到底这也是社团活动的一环
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种不同于商用成品 独一无二的手工小饰品
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}意外受人们欢迎哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗 这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快看快看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.61,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大海
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日本的大海也就那样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好想游泳
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.79,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 我们可不是来玩的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.62,0:06:26.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}分头找找能用的东西吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别走太远哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}治子老师 还有什么要补充的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}捡贝壳和玻璃碎片的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}注意别伤到手
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.28,0:06:38.92,Dial_CH,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}明白
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.58,Dial_CH,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}知道喵
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也请须理出多多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯…好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}各自去寻找素材吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do It
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}路上小心
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像这样的 多找几个组合起来
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做成饰品或许很可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 再多找点
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这也能用吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把这种管子组装起来
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.86,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以做一些室内装饰
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蒸汽朋克
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.85,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是部长亲
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个也能用上吗喵
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.22,0:07:48.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做成从房顶挂下来的装饰怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感觉很时髦喵
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些是玛瑙
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些是海玻璃
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good 好像能用
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把这些贝壳组合起来 或许能做成发圈
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.45,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发现了奇怪的石头
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来是海参
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是作为土特产带回去
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.13,0:08:23.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妈妈和三代目会很高兴吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海参的佐料
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我开动了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有更多海参吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.09,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 海参
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你干什么来了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}布丁也一起来找海参吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这算是非法捕猎吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不行吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再见 海参
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别再被抓了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的 塞璐芙
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.72,0:09:12.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她这样真能在DIY部待下去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.32,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}形状奇怪的木头
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.55,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个能做成什么吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.03,0:09:29.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部长同学
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.37,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很不错的流木啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.76,0:09:40.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 形状很有趣 应该能用它做点什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}利用它这个形状
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做成帽子架怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或许不错
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.17,0:09:52.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过 这个流木太大了带不回去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稍等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.59,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了 这样就能带回去了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是部长…同学
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}手法真好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}熟能生巧罢了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}熟能生巧？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塞璐芙好像不管过多久都不会变巧啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也不全是如此
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最近也慢慢学会用一些道具了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}伤口也比以前少很多了对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}带回去用锉刀磨一下就能用了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剩下的部分我可以拿走吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 请便
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全勤奖哦 塞璐芙同学
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被贝壳划伤手了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.52,0:10:47.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}治子姐姐的便当真好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.75,0:10:51.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽说布丁妈妈做的萩饼也很好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这也称得上是Good job
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}多吃一点哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之后怎么说
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}素材已经收集了不少了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还想再多找点
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或许能找到更好的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}布丁也会一起来找的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}陪你们一会也不是不行
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是须理出亲喵
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}难得来一趟
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.45,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再去找一些东西吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哦 哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等我下
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看招
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概就这样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找到了不少嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}靠这些可以做很多东西吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 我很期待
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做什么好呢喵
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来玩吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玩？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.83,0:12:03.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.20,0:12:09.55,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}堆个沙雕城堡 游个泳 再晒个日光浴
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后 然后…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的 来到海边就想堆沙雕城堡
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算要游泳 泳衣怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}泳衣的话没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就想到会这样 其实是穿着泳衣来的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这家伙
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.59,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个 那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其实 我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}匠匠也是？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是没办法呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 我也奉陪一下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.74,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}JOB子也
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}衣服下面当然是泳衣啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么叫当然
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.76,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过 我也穿来了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.76,0:12:57.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.58,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都不必多说了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如此一来…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.04,0:13:09.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我…我只是被拉过来的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.38,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}泳衣什么的怎么可能…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.36,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}穿着哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.18,0:13:17.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早上你在镜子前面臭美 我可都看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是须理出亲喵
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家想的都一样吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我好在意布丁的泳衣
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.06,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让我看看让我看看
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.35,Dial_CH2,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}别害羞嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.35,Dial_CH2,,0,800,0,,{\blur4}等下
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let’s go baby
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你没有带水蜘蛛来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.61,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}七忍具之一
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.06,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我怎么可能有那种东西
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小JOB子 水遁术的话我会哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.58,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用通气管对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.69,0:13:54.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}各就各位
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.85,0:13:58.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}预备
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.79,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}两…两者不相上下
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希 希同学胜
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.86,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们俩都好快
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.86,0:14:34.86,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她们在搞什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.62,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}天气暖和可真不错
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然水还有点凉
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是呀 很舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看看刚刚的海参还在不在
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.11,0:15:02.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海参可不会带你到龙宫去
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.61,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嘛 都被你看透了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.61,0:15:10.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管我在想什么 布丁马上就能知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.86,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然了 你在想什么还不简单
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.32,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么「真厉害」啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚刚的语气好像
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再来一次
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.06,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.55,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再来一次嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要就是不要
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}结束
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.47,0:15:36.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日本宫殿 干得漂亮 匠
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们俩的努力没白费呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.93,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水和沙子的比例很重要
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.93,0:15:48.32,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然实际是掺了粘土来固定地基
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希 那边是
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}特别是瓦片的细节…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的老天
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢 布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.04,0:16:17.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好久没给我扎过头发了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我自己扎的话没一会就松了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为你很笨
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天布丁也一块来 真是太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…是嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.76,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我说啊 布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.90,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也加入DIY部吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.79,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然不是一个高中的 但是小希也得到入部许可了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.79,0:16:54.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也入部的话就又能每天一起回家了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然你说DIY是发了霉的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我想你会不会对DIY稍有兴趣了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.01,0:17:06.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塞璐芙亲 须理出亲
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一起来玩喵
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 这就来
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}走吧 布丁
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就算了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.32,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找材料找得有点累了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.85,0:17:37.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嘛 那一会见
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.84,0:17:38.37,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把这个送给塞璐芙的话她会不会开心呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 住手
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.58,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}疼死了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你没抹防晒霜吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太瞧不起太阳了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.69,0:18:44.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看我准备完全就一点事都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.54,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好烦 早知道这样我…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不去就好了？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可没这么说过
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.70,0:18:55.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也不是不开心
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说啥 我听不见
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么都没说
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.97,0:19:10.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好嘞
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完工了喵
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}连我自己都觉得这是杰作
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完事记得给我弄回去
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.24,0:19:19.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我准备用海玻璃做一个手链
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要给这个钻眼吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.47,0:19:32.85,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}先在海玻璃上沾一点水
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么要用水
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.49,0:19:38.26,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为钻的时候会有玻璃粉飞出来
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玻璃也容易受热变脆
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要开始钻了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.38,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等水滴浑浊变成白色之后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就用水轻轻冲一下
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.54,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等钻到八成左右
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.32,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再把金刚石钻头换成两毫米的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后从反方向继续钻
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}钻通之后给玻璃涂上树脂胶
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再放到紫外灯下固化
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最后给海玻璃和珠子穿上线
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}手链就做好了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}匠匠真厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}简直就跟店里卖的那些一样
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good job 匠
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.29,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}匠亲 你手好巧喵
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.52,0:20:33.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个品相 放到哪里都不怕比
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗 那太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那咱们到底怎么卖？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}挂网上卖吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不光要在日本卖 更要远销四海喵
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全世界的订单都纷至沓来
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.20,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你那个就是痴人说梦了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.60,0:20:56.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}除了挂网上还可以去文化节…那得等秋天了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.74,0:20:57.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}摆地摊呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有那种能出租货架的杂货铺
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以在那边卖手工艺品
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.45,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个点子也不错
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一会 那放在我家店里说不定也行
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放在WAKUWAKU WANWAN里吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想去看一看WAKUWAN
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想去部长亲家里喵
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以 没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.54,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一起来我家玩吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.67,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下雨了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.29,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放在这里恰到好处
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第一次就做得这么好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}手里还有一些海玻璃和贝壳
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.76,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用这些能做个小摆设
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.36,0:21:54.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 我这是干什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}得去学习了
